### GitVitals - Instructor API Testing
### Use this file with REST Client VS Code extension or similar HTTP client

@baseUrl = https://gitvitals-zurq-691xoogso-mrauto-cats-projects.vercel.app
@apiBase = {{baseUrl}}/api/instructor

### 1. Get All Submissions (No Filters)
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get Submissions - Filter by Reading Number
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions?readingNumber=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Get Submissions - Filter by Graded Status (Ungraded Only)
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions?graded=false
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Get Submissions - Filter by Cohort
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions?cohort=Fall2025
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. Get Submissions - With Pagination
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions?limit=10&offset=0
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 6. Get Submissions - Date Range Filter
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-01-31
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 7. Get Submissions - Combined Filters
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions?readingNumber=1&graded=false&cohort=Fall2025
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 8. Get Roster for Assignment (Reading Number Required)
GET {{apiBase}}/roster?readingNumber=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 9. Get Roster - Filter by Cohort
GET {{apiBase}}/roster?readingNumber=1&cohort=Fall2025
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 10. Get Roster - Filter by Patient
GET {{apiBase}}/roster?readingNumber=1&patientId=PATIENT_UUID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 11. Get Student History (Replace {id} with student UUID)
GET {{apiBase}}/students/STUDENT_UUID_HERE/history
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 12. Get Student History - Filter by Reading Number
GET {{apiBase}}/students/STUDENT_UUID_HERE/history?readingNumber=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 13. Get Specific Submission (Replace {id} with submission UUID)
GET {{apiBase}}/submissions/SUBMISSION_UUID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 14. DB Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/db
Content-Type: application/json

###
